gmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:20:31.000Z","msg":"我講咗好多次我唔係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"時下局勢,  請問你會唔會相信警員講既野 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662f80a5c0bac88478c90c10a424883bb98ec43b","tid":1323004,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71bdc823cbc6779afc6ed3bb5c673ba600bfb30a","tid":1323004,"uid":256783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"994ccb93da84902a913e93960c496d1f3b66c642","tid":1323004,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4b5f7f51a405f76a05ebba6e468dc5458273f6e9","tid":1323004,"uid":256783,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:10:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽講樓主係警員</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:20:31.000Z","msg":"我講咗好多次我唔係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"時下局勢,  請問你會唔會相信警員講既野 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:25:31.000Z","msg":"我只係知道依家有警察親人好驚， 因為佢所期望嘅示威者同實際上表現出嚟嘅示威者唔同，已經遠超佢哋控制。<br />\n所以好急要搵一班人帶風向， 唔想自己親人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n我相信再係咁升級落去持續多半年，應該會有兵變或者辭職潮。"},{"pid":"b2e4d376dc24322258bbaf694ce48711fae143c3","tid":1323004,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:27:28.000Z","msg":"都係嗰句， 做警察係貪佢薪金高糧準 冇危險。<br />\n<br />\n若果風險大到係會殘廢或者喪生嘅話，我相信好多人寧願唔做。 或者揸流灘咁做。<br />\n<br />\n絕對會少咗好多單拖衝入人群嘅勇武警察"},{"pid":"6ad710f042b74f778fa3ccf17856913ea4f17510","tid":1323004,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39408fd2cf2ebdb656d062a62abeacb4dce4a3ac","tid":1323004,"uid":259700,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:28:43.000Z","msg":"200萬人支持撤回反送中條例， 若果有任何人做任何事達到目的，呢二百萬人相信都會支持。<br />\n因為呢樣嘢牽涉香港人嘅自由。"},{"pid":"dcd97f50dbc65f206528e7eab3218e